Package cs2030.simulator

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Customer
    Abstract Customer class representing customers where each customer has his/her own unique id, state and arrivalTime.
    Event
    Event class representing events(actions) of the system, where each event has a Customer, time and a Server.
    EventComparator
    EventComparator class implements the logic of comparing 2 events by time (smaller time given priority), if both events have the same time, they are compared by customer id (smaller id given priority).
    GreedyCustomer
    GreedyCustomer class, extending Customer, representing greedy customer in the simulator.
    Server
    An abstract class representing a Server object that can serve customers in the simulator.
    Simulator
    Simulator class encompassing the logic of the simulator program, where each Simulator has its own queue of events, list of servers, random generator and statistics.
    Statistics
    Statistics class representing the statistics to collect.
    TypicalCustomer
    TypicalCustomer class, extending Customer, representing typical customer in the simulator.
